{"id":232822275,"title":"公館抹布阿伯","content":"大家有遇過這個阿伯嗎\n最近在前門誠品附近\n常常看到一個阿伯坐在滑板車上\n似乎是行動不便者，所以用「手」走路，行動緩慢\n一手推推車，一手拿抹布，有人經過就把手舉起來示意要不要買\n經過的人不是快速側身路過就是默默遠離他走到人行道那側\n因爲已經看到不少次了\n所以剛剛經過就去買了一包\n\n其實我能理解大家看到這種弱勢人士可能會有點怕怕的或怕被坑錢\n不過大家對阿伯視而不見還是讓我有點難過\n\n一包100裡面有三個大抹布，其實不貴QQ\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/34f37241-baa3-4468-a832-b26a24746a5c/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/94705c67-43fd-4596-8652-cad0ca09907d/1280.jpeg\n希望大家下次看到時可以幫忙一下～\n讓社會多一點溫暖\n\n大家期末加油！","excerpt":"大家有遇過這個阿伯嗎，最近在前門誠品附近，常常看到一個阿伯坐在滑板車上，似乎是行動不便者，所以用「手」走路，行動緩慢，一手推推車，一手拿抹布，有人經過就把手舉起來示意要不要買，經過的人不是快速側身路過","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"3c91f2b0-6374-4467-b557-2e5383680afb","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-04T04:56:34.368Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-04T04:58:50.419Z","commentCount":68,"likeCount":67,"tags":[],"topics":["公館","抹布","阿伯"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"臺灣大學","forumAlias":"ntu","school":"國立臺灣大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":66},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/34f37241-baa3-4468-a832-b26a24746a5c/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/94705c67-43fd-4596-8652-cad0ca09907d/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c9bb1c52-b379-418f-8380-f445ae977a5d","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/34f37241-baa3-4468-a832-b26a24746a5c/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/34f37241-baa3-4468-a832-b26a24746a5c/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/34f37241-baa3-4468-a832-b26a24746a5c/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-04T04:56:34.36